         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">10/10/82. ¶  ¶ I had mislaid the specimen from Port Victor, ¶  dear Mr Tepper, it is  ¶ Pseudanthus micranthus ¶  Benth. ¶  ¶ Do not let yourself be hindered in sending your paper on the lerp insect t...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">82.10.10a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Otto Tepper</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">RB MSS M198, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne. </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS annotation by Tepper: 'Reply 16.10.82'. Letter not found.</p>
               </note>10/10/82.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich hatte das Ex. von Pt. Victor verlegt, lieber Herr Tepper, es ist <name key="Pseudanthus%20micranthus">Pseudanthus micranthus</name>, Bth. </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Lassen Sie sich nicht hindern Ihre Abhandlung an die L.S. zu senden über das Lerp Insekt, nachdem Sie sich auf Mr Dobson u Prof. Anderson bezogen.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Ihr</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">10/10/82.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I had mislaid the specimen from Port Victor,<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Encounter Bay, SA. See O. Tepper to M, 2 October 1882 (in this edition as 82-10-02b).</p>
               </note> dear Mr Tepper, it is <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Pseudanthus%20micranthus">Pseudanthus micranthus</name>
               </seg> Benth.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Do not let yourself be hindered in sending your paper on the lerp insect to the Linnean Society after you referred to Mr Dobson and Professor Anderson.<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>i.e. Dobson (1851) and Anderson (1851), of which M subsequently lent Tepper copies; see M to O. Tepper, 21 October 1882 (in this edition as 82-10-21b). Tepper (1884) was read on 15 February 1883; the printed paper has an addendum, derived from a letter to the Society, that acknowledges these two papers that 'Baron von Mueller has kindly sent me', and concludes that 'neither of the two Lerp insects therein described are identical with that observed by myself'. </p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller. </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Pseudanthus%20micranthus">Pseudanthus micranthus</name>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
         </div>
